chapter Disjunction
Introduce the "or" or "disjuction" connective, ∨.

statement ∨ (φ ψ) definition (→ ¬ φ ψ)

theorem Add Right Disjunct
premise φ
prove → ¬ φ ψ
prove ∨ φ ψ
qed

theorem Add Left Disjunct
premise ψ
prove → ¬ φ ψ
prove ∨ φ ψ
qed

